# Web (Next.js) rules

- App Router only (`web/app/`); do not use `pages/`
- Backend URL via `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` (default `http://localhost:8080`)
- Tailwind CSS is available; keep styles in globals.css or inline className
- Keep components in `web/app/`; extract to `web/components/` only when reused 2+
- Run: `cd web && npm run dev` → `http://localhost:3000`
- No new npm packages without explicit approval
- TypeScript: strict mode, no `any` unless truly unavoidable
